-- out/todo.txt --
issue4251_notC, issue4251_notB, issue4251_notB_reversed: these are only evaluated correctly by v3.
cyclicalInsertInDisjunction.err1: should be an error for both evaluators but both produce concrete values.
preseveBottomSemantics: both evaluators are incorrect; result should be _ or _|{}.
